22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20he%20could%20live%20in%20forever%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20speaks%20volumes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2283aaea92-af24-49a8-8826-9ecfccc72407%5C%22%3ETokyo%20is%20a%20crowded%20city%20with%20pockets%20of%20tranquility%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20me%2C%20Tokyo%20is%20a%20city%20of%20contradictions.%20It's%20a%20place%20that%20can%20provide%20both%20sensory%20overload%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20serene%20tranquility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I%20can%20be%20shoulder-to-shoulder%20with%20hundreds%20of%20strangers%20on%20the%20train%2C%20and%20then%20moments%20later%20find%20myself%20in%20a%20quiet%20garden.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20the%20entire%20world%20is%20on%20top%20of%20me%2C%20and%20then%20suddenly%2C%20I%20have%20the%20whole%20world%20to%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETokyo%20seems%20to%20thrive%20on%20organized%20chaos%20%E2%80%94%20the%20flashing%20neon%20lights%2C%20the%20bustling%20crowds%2C%20and%20the%20hum%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-so-many-vending-machines-in-japan-2017-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evending%20machines%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20dispense%20everything%20from%20hot%20coffee%20to%20canned%20corn%20soup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20place%20that%20attacks%20my%20senses%20but%20somehow%20soothes%20my%20soul%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f9ea91f-3cf8-4060-bbcb-bda9cb0181f8%5C%22%3EThe%20work%20culture%20is%20a%20double-edged%20sword%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sun%20sets%20over%20Tokyo%20skyscrapers%20on%20a%20cloudy%20day.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d45d24585f1dff88b231e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20work%20culture%20in%20Japan%20can%20be%20intense.%3Cp%3EMarshall%20Gunnell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20leaving%20the%20US%2C%20I%20felt%20stuck%20in%20the%20relentless%20work%