possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDear%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbookmyshow%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40bookmyshow%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20I%20still%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20have%20your%20platform%20or%20no.%3Cbr%3E%5CnBelow%20is%20humble%20view%20-%3Cbr%3E%5CnTo%20the%20audiences%20I'm%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20boycotts%20or%20down%20rating%20a%20private%20business%E2%80%A6%3Cbr%3E%5CnBook%20my%20show%20is%20well%20within%20their%20right%20to%20do%20what's%20best%20for%20their%20business%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTXaB22sfxI%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FTXaB22sfxI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Kunal%20Kamra%20(%40kunalkamra88)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkunalkamra88%2Fstatus%2F1909195974318215341%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%207%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20issue%20at%20hand%20isn't%20about%20whether%20you%20can%20or%20will%20delist%20me%20-%20it's%20about%20your%20exclusive%20right%20on%20listing%20our%20shows.%20By%20not%20allowing%20artists%20to%20list%20their%20shows%20through%20their%20own%20websites%2C%20you've%20effectively%20prevented%20me%20from%20accessing%20the%20audience%20I've%20performed%20for%20from%202017%20to%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ticketing%20platform%2C%20run%20by%20Bigtree%20Entertainment%20Private%20Limited%2C%20has%20removed%20Kunal%20Kamra's%20content%20and%20delisted%20him%20amid%20a%20massive%20row%20over%20his%20jokes%20against%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20and%20Maharashtra's%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde.%20In%20a%20show%20at%20Mumbai's%20Habitat%20studio%2C%20the%20comic%20sang%20a%20parody%20of%20'Bholi%20Si%20Surat'%2C%20a%20popular%20song%20from%20the%20Bollywood%20movie%20'Dil%20To%20Pagal%20Hai'.%20The%20lyrics%20targeted%20Mr%20Shinde%2C%20referring%20to%20him%20as%20'gaddar'%20(traitor).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shinde%20led%20the%20rebellion%20that%20split%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20toppled%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government%20in%202022.%20Mr%20Thackeray%20has%20often%20used%20the%20'gaddar'%20insult%20against%20his%20former%20lieutenant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfuriated%20by%20Kamra's%20remarks%2C%20Mr%20Shinde's%20supporters%20vandalised%20the%20Habitat%20studio%2C%20a%20preferred%20venue%20for%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows.%20The%20studio%20in%20Khar%20subsequently%20shut%20down%2C%20stressing%20that%20it%20exercises%20no%20control%20over%20the%20content%20of%20any%20show.%20Parts%20of%20the%20studio%20were%20demolished%20the%20next%20day%2C%20with%20civic%20authorities%20citing%20building%20law%20violations.%20But%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20action%20has%20sparked%20a%20buzz%20that%20the%20action%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20Kunal%20Kamra%20controversy.%20Multiple%20cases%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20the%20comic.%20He%20has%20skipped%20three%20summons%20and%20the%20Madras%20High%20Court%20has%20provided%20him%20interim%20protection%20from%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20take%20a%2010%25%20cut%20of%20the%20revenue%20for%20listing%20shows%2C%20which%20is%20your%20business%20model.%20However%2C%20this%20raises%20an%20important%20point%3A%20No%20matter%20how%20big%20or%20small%20a%20comedian%20is%2C%20we%20are%20all%20compelled%20to%20spend%20between%206%2C000%20to%2010%2C000%20rupees%20a%20day%20on%20advertising%20to%20reach%20our%20own%20audience.%20This%20cost%20is%20an%20additional%20burden%20that%20we%2C%20as%20artists%2C%20must%20bear%2C%26quot%3B%20Kunal%20Kamra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comic%20then%20made%20a%20request.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I'm%20requesting%20is%20simple%3A%20please%20ensure%20that%20you%20hand%20over%20the%20contact%20information%20of%20the%20audiences%20you've%20collected%20from%20my%20solo%20shows%20so%20that%20I%20can%20continue%20living%20my%20life%20with%20dignity%20and%20work%20towards%20a%20fair%20livelihood.%20As%20a%20solo%20artist%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20world%20of%20comedy%2C%20we%20are%20both%20the%20show%20and%20the%20production.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20I%20performed%20at%20the%20Pune%20Comedy%20Festival%20with%2030%20other%20artists%2C%20that%20would%20be%20considered%20comedy's%20collective%20data.%20But%20my%20solo%20shows%20-%20that's%20my%20audience.%20The%20least%20I%20deserve%2C%20should%20you%20choose%20to%20delist%20me%2C%20is%20access%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20request%20one%20of%20the%20following%3A%20Do%20not%20delist%20me%2C%20or%20Provide%20me%20with%20the%20data%20(contact%20information)%20I've%20generated%20through%20your%20platform%20from%20my%20audience.%20Thank%20you%20for%20your%20understanding%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Kunal%20Kamra%20said%20while%20the%20portal%20may%20argue%20that%20data%20protection%20is%20a%20concern%2C%20'the%20question%20of%20who%20protects%20what%20data%2C%20and%20from%20whom%2C%20is%20a%20much%20broader%20conversation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Sena%20leader%20Rahool%20Kanal%20had%20urged%20BookMyShow%20not%20to%20provide%20a%20platform%20to%20Kunal%20Jamra.%20Following%20the%20portal's%20delisting%20move%2C%20Rahool%20Kanal%2C%20who%20was%20among%20the%2012%20Sena%20leaders%20arrested%20in%20a%20vandalism%20case%2C%20thanked%20the%20ticketing%20platform.%20%26quot%3BThank%20you%20for%20keeping%20your%20portal%20clean%20and%20keeping%20such%20artists%20out%20of%20the%20list%20of%20pure%20entertainment%2C%20because%20we%20all%20being%20Mumbaikars%20love%20and%20believe%20in%20every%20form%20of%20art%20but%20not%20personal%20agendas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744024320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fi7bail9c_kunal-kamra-bms_625x300_07_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F