rtificial%20intelligence.%20It%20will%20be%20available%20to%20students%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202025%20as%20one%20of%2021%20MBA%20majors%20alongside%20options%20like%20accounting%2C%20finance%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20real%20estate.%20For%20undergraduates%20who%20earn%20a%20degree%20in%20economics%2C%20it'll%20be%20one%20of%2019%20concentrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20curriculum%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewill%20help%20students%20develop%20both%20a%20technical%20understanding%20of%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-artificial-intelligence-customer-experience-business-applications-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebusinesses%20are%20using%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20more%20conceptual%20sense%20of%20the%20technology's%20economic%2C%20social%2C%20and%20ethical%20implications.%20Students%20will%20be%20required%20to%20take%20classes%20in%20machine%20learning%20and%20ethics%20and%20choose%20from%20a%20list%20of%20electives%20spanning%20data%20mining%20to%20marketing%20to%20neuroscience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20required%20courses%20will%20be%20%26quot%3BBig%20Data%2C%20Big%20Responsibilities%3A%20Toward%20Accountable%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20ethics%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFoundations%20of%20Deep%20Learning%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20a%20new%20class%20in%20the%20statistics%20and%20data%20science%20department%2C%20giving%20students%20an%20introduction%20to%20the%20technical%20foundations%20of%20AI%2C%20Wharton%20professor%20Giles%20Hooker%2C%20an%20advisor%20for%20the%20new%20AI%20curriculum%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20by%20email.%20It%20will%20cover%20the%20technology%20underpinning%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-data-centers-hyperscalers-bubble-outlook-alibaba-tech-nvidia-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20topics%20from%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20is%20a%20neural%20network%20and%20how%20to%20train%20it%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bgenerative%20AI%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Befficient%20deep%20learning%26quot%3B%20to%20ensure%20students%20have%20%26quot%3Ba%20solid%20conceptual%20grasp%20on%20what%20goes%20on%20under%20the%20hood%20in%20modern%20AI%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20syllabus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWharton%20also%20updated%20the%20syllabi%20for%20existing%20classes%2C%20including%20the%20management%20course%20%26quot%3BInnovation%2C%20Change%2C%20and%20Entrepreneurship%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20marketing%20course%20%26quot%3BIntroduction%20to%20Brain%20Science%20for%20Business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20university%20press%20release%20announcing%20the%20changes%2C%20Eric%20Bradlow%2C%20the%20vice%20dean%20of%20AI%20and%20Analytics%20at%20Wharton%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20at%20a%20critical%20turning%20point%20where%20practical%20AI%20knowledge%20is%20urgently%20needed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20are%20struggling%20to%20recruit%20talent%20with%20the%20necessary%20AI%20skills%2C%20students%20are%20eager%20to%20deepen%20their%20understanding%20of%20the%20subject%20and%20gain%20hands-on%20experience%2C%20and%20our%20faculty's%20expertise%20on%20the%20adoption%20and%20human%20impact%20of%20AI%20is%20unmatched%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213f4478f-86b2-4071-b7c9-62084ec6eb49%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20intersection%20of%20AI%20and%20business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWharton%20faculty%20began%20discussing%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20new%20AI%20curriculum%20last%20year%2C%20Hooker%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202024%2C%20Wharton%20launched%20the%20AI%20and%20Analytics%20Initiative%20to%20study%20possible%20changes%20to%20its%20curriculum%2C%20invest%20in%20new%20research%2C%20collaborate%20more%20with%20industries%2C%20and%20create%20open-source%20generative%20AI%20resources%2C%20according%20to%20Penn%20Today%2C%20the%20university's%20official%20news%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20initiative%2C%20Wharton%20has%20launched%20the%20AI%20Research%20Fund%20to%20help%20faculty%20pursue%20research%20at%20the%20intersection%20of%20AI%20and%20business%20and%20the%20Education%20Innovation%20Fund%20to%20help%20faculty%20adopt%20AI%20in%20the%20classroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20was%20also%20used%20to%20provide%20ChatGPT%20Enterprise%20licenses%20to%20all%20full-time%20and%20executive%20MBA%20students%20starting%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202024%20%E2%80%94%20a%20first-of-its-kind%20collaboration%20between%20a%20business%20school%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistory-of-openai-company-chatgpt-elon-musk-founded-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Wharton%20unveiled%20the%20Accountable%20AI%20Lab%2C%20which%20will%20produce%20research%20on%20AI%20governance%2C%20regulation%2C%20and%20ethics%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bpractical%20focus%20on%20business%20applications.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWharton%20therefore%20had%20several%20building%20blocks%20in%20place%20for%20a%20new%20curriculum%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHooker%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20what%20we%20had%20to%20do%20was%20to%20work%20out%20how%20to%20structure%20a%20useful%20and%20coherent%20path%20through%20what%20we%20offered%20and%20then%20see%20if%20there%20was%20anything%20we%20really%20needed%20to%20add%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudents%20who%20graduate%20with%20an%20AI%20focus%20will%20ideally%20be%20adept%20in%20four%20areas%2C%20Hooker%20said.%20They'll%20have%20a%20strong%20technical%20knowledge%20of%20AI%20to%20assess%20the%20design%20and%20application%20of%20AI%20models%20in%20a%20business%20and%20be%20informed%20enough%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20new%20AI%20developments.%20They'll%20have%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20AI%20will%20impact%20business%20operations.%20They'll%20also%20have%20a%20handle%20on%20the%20ethics%20of%20data%20and%20automated%20decision-making%20and%20understand%20the%20legal%20frameworks%20governing%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20these%20days%20are%20hiring%20candidates%20who%20specialize%20in%20just%20one%20of%20these%20areas.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20company%20might%20hire%20an%20AI%20researcher%20to%20train%20large%20language%20models%2C%20a%20learning%20and%20development%20expert%20to%20teach%20teams%20how%20to%20use%20the%20technology%20or%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chief-ethics-officer-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawyer%20who%20understands%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chief-ethics-officer-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20data%20privacy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20graduates%20of%20Wharton's%20new%20program%20may%20emerge%20as%20a%20jack-of-all-AI-trades.%20Their%20skill%20sets%20will%20be%20tailored%20to%20a%20future%20workplace%20where%20adaptability%20might%20be%20more%20valuable%20than%20specialization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20the%20impact%20of%20AI%20on%20business%20to%20be%20long%20and%20deep.%20Even%20without%20new%20breakthroughs%20in%20human-like%20reasoning%2C%20we%20can%20expect%20AI%20methods%20to%20penetrate%20even%20further%20into%20business%20processes%20and%20our%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20Hooker%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20careers%20and%20job%20titles%20associated%20with%20its%20penetration%20into%20business%20haven't%20yet%20been%20fixed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwharton-business-school-upenn-ai-curriculum-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744022703000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f0266663d72727e199427a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwharton-business-school-upenn-ai-c