3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20kept%20my%20pantry%20stocked%20so%20I%20could%20fairly%20easily%20try%20new%20recipes.%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20new%20recipes%20to%20throw%20in%20the%20mix%20helped%20me%20prevent%20boredom%20in%20the%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20month%2C%20I%20tried%20lots%20of%20new%20recipes%2C%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ambitiouskitchen.com%2Fcarrot-arugula-salad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarrot-and-arugula%20salad%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsallysbakingaddiction.com%2Fcrispy-coconut-chicken-with-spicy-honey-orange-sauce%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoconut-crusted%20chicken%20tenders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.recipetineats.com%2Frosemary-garlic-lamb-cutlets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elamb%20cutlets%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20are%20now%20in%20our%20regular%20rotation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20keeping%20fruits%20and%20veggies%20in%20the%20freezer%20and%20staples%20like%20seeds%2C%20nuts%2C%20beans%2C%20and%20legumes%20in%20the%20pantry%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20throw%20together%20simple%20dinners%20when%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20estimate%20I%20saved%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20just%20from%20one%20month%20of%20eating%20at%20home.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Salad%20with%20carrot%2C%20arugula%2C%20avocado%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d8915e585f1dff88b264f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBy%20cooking%20at%20home%2C%20I%20used%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20produce%20I%20otherwise%20would've%20let%20go%20bad.%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20partner%20and%20I%20typically%20dine%20out%20casually%20one%20to%20three%20times%20a%20week%20(about%20%2430%20to%20%2450%20each%20time)%2C%20and%20go%20on%20a%20nicer%20date%20night%20around%20once%20a%20month%20(easily%20%24150%20to%20%24300%20a%20meal).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%2C%20I'd%20estimate%20we%20usually%20spend%20at%20least%20%24100%20on%20dining%20out%20a%20week%20in%20addition%20to%20regular%20grocery%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGroceries%20certainly%20aren't%20cheap%20right%20now%2C%20but%20when%20they%20were%20our%20only%20food%20expense%20this%20month%2C%20we%20saved%20so%20much%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20to%20my%20surprise%2C%20our%20grocery%20spending%20(typically%20around%20%2470%20to%20%24120%20a%20week)%20didn't%20increase%20much%20over%20the%20month%20%E2%80%94%20probably%20because%20I%20spent%20more%20time%20planning%20our%20meals.%20We%20also%20wasted%20less%20food.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20lot%20easier%20to%20not%20let%20produce%20go%20bad%20or%20forget%20about%20it%20when%20you're%20pushing%20yourself%20to%20cook%20every%20meal%20at%20home%20and%20not%20giving%20yourself%20an%20easy%20out%20by%20ordering%20delivery%20from%20a%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAbout%20halfway%20through%20the%20experiment%2C%20I%20noticed%20I%20started%20feeling%20better%2C%20too.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Salad%20with%20couscous%2C%20zucchini%2C%20lemon%2C%20feta%2C%20cucumber%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d8903ab8b41a9673fae6ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20found%20myself%20eating%20a%20lot%20of%20veggies%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20consuming%20if%20I'd%20been%20dining%20out.%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20month%2C%20I%20loaded%20up%20on%20a%20lot%20more%20veggies%20and%20fruit%20than%20I%20would've%20had%20I%20been%20regularly%20dining%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20a%20lot%20more%20energy%20toward%20the%20latter%20half%20of%20the%20month%2C%20which%20I%20attributed%20partially%20to%20the%20healthier%20meals%20(and%20partially%20to%20some%20warmer%2C%20spring-like%20weather).%20I%20found%20I%20was%20able%20to%20go%20for%20longer%20walks%20and%20spend%20more%20time%20at%20the%20gym%20than%20usual%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20also%20argue%20having%20mocktails%20at%20home%20instead%20of%20ordering%20cocktails%20out%20contributed%20to%20my%20feeling%20better%20physically%20over%20the%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20from%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%20cooking-from-home%20experiment%2C%20I%20lost%20about%2010%20pounds%20and%20felt%20much%20better%20mentally%20and%20physically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20I'd%20considered%20this%20month%20a%20success.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sliced%20fruit%20in%20a%20bowl%20with%20pumpkin%20seeds%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d891bb69253ccddf998058%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOverall%2C%20we%20saved%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20this%20month%20by%20not%20dining%20out.%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20month%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-only-eat-at-home-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeating%20only%20home-cooked%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20saved%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20and%20felt%20much%20more%20energized%2C%20but%20I%20never%20felt%20left%20out%20of%20any%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20dining%20out%2C%20but%20this%20process%20reminded%20my%20partner%20just%20how%20much%20we%20could%20save%20by%20making%20meals%20at%20home.%20I%20feel%20inspired%20to%20save%20going%20to%20restaurants%20for%20fewer%2C%20more%20special%20occasions%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20now%20that%20I've%20added%20so%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-easy-recipes-to-make-air-fryer-chef-favorites%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreat%20recipes%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20our%20repertoire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20cooking%20can%20still%20feel%20like%20a%20chore%2C%20I%20learned%20combining%20new%20recipes%20with%20repeat%20staples%20is%20my%20ideal%20way%20to%20keep%20meals%20feeling%20exciting%20and%20appealing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20I%20realized%20just%20how%20much%20leaning%20on%20premade%20ingredients%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-jarred-tomato-sauce-to-buy-reviewed-photos-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejarred%20sauces%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20frozen%20flatbreads%2C%20can%20make%20cooking%20more%20accessible%2C%20especially%20on%20busy%20nights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20these%20results%20were%20so%20impressive%20that%20it's%20already%20been%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonly-ate-home-cooked-food-for-a-month-what-happened-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecook%20more%20meals%20at%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20month%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcooked-meals-at-home-month-how-it-went-tips-dishes-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744022161000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67db2f74585f1dff88b2a5d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcooked-meals-at-home-month-how-it-went-tips-dishes-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20tried%20to%20cook%20all%20of%20my%20meals%20at%20home%20for%20a%20month.%20I%20saved%20money%2C%20felt%20better%2C%20lost%20weight%2C%20and%20learned%20great%20tips%20and%20easy%20dinner%20recipes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Paige%20Bennett)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcooked-meals-at-hom