ng%20and%20dubbing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBI%20got%20an%20exclusive%20look%20at%20the%20pitch%20deck%20used%20to%20secure%20the%20fresh%20funding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EVoice%20intelligence%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpyannoteai-funding-voice-ai-france-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPyannoteAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20just%20raised%20%249%20million%20in%20a%20seed%20round%20led%20by%20Crane%20Ventures%20and%20Serena.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20startup%2C%20launched%20in%202024%2C%20has%20developed%20an%20AI%20model%20for%20a%20concept%20called%20%26quot%3Bspeaker%20diarization.%26quot%3B%20It's%20the%20process%20of%20enhancing%20audio%20transcriptions%20to%20distinguish%20between%20different%20speakers%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20AI%20has%20historically%20struggled%20with.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20mission%20is%20to%20make%20human%20and%20AI%20interactions%20natural%20through%20voice%2C%26quot%3B%20Vincent%20Molina%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20voice%20AI%20industry%20today%20mostly%20focuses%20on%20one-to-one%20conversations%20between%20humans%20and%20AI.%20But%20real-life%20conversations%20aren't%20like%20that.%20They're%20full%20of%20multi-speaker%20situations%2C%20overlapping%20speech%2C%20interruptions%2C%20and%20short%20and%20chaotic%20speech%20turns%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup's%20platform%20aims%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20AI%20model%20not%20only%20picks%20up%20on%20an%20accurate%20audio%20transcription%20but%20also%20understands%20who%20is%20speaking%20and%20their%20intonation.%20The%20intended%20result%20is%20for%20AI%20to%20preserve%20the%20meaning%20of%20audio%20across%20different%20languages%20and%20use%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20was%20developed%20using%20research%20conducted%20by%20the%20startup's%20cofounder%2C%20Herv%C3%A9%20Bredin%2C%20who%20has%20authored%20over%2030%20papers%20on%20the%20topic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPyannoteAI's%20enterprise%20use%20cases%20include%20indexing%20large-scale%20audio%20for%20media%20platforms%2C%20streamlining%20the%20dubbing%20process%2C%20and%20transcribing%20consultations%20across%20enterprise%20and%20healthcare.%20It%20counts%20Gladia%20and%20MediVox%20as%20its%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvoice-ai-vc-startups-tech-innovation-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVoice%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20gained%20significant%20traction%20in%20the%20past%20year%2C%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20ElevenLabs%20and%20PolyAI%20raising%20significant%20rounds%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMolina%20said%20his%20startup%20had%20increased%20investor%20interest%20from%20both%20Europe%20and%20the%20US.%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20voice%20AI%20landscape%20is%20accelerating%20%E2%80%94%20across%20all%20layers%3A%20infrastructure%2C%20applications%2C%20models%2C%20and%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BSince%20we're%20positioned%20at%20the%20very%20beginning%20of%20the%20value%20chain%2C%20and%20because%20we%20serve%20the%20entire%20ecosystem%2C%20we%20received%20strong%20interest%20from%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20investors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20funding%20confirms%20BI's%20November%20report%20that%20PyannoteAI%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpyannoteai-funding-voice-ai-france-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20talks%20to%20raise%20about%20%2410%20million%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Crane%20Ventures%20and%20Serena%2C%20PyannoteAI's%20funding%20round%20had%20participation%20from%20Julien%20Chaumond%2C%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20of%20HuggingFace%2C%20and%20former%20Meta%20and%20OpenAI%20researcher%20Alexis%20Conneau.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20fresh%20funding%2C%20the%20startup%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20grow%20its%20research%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20out