r-heart-attack-part-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20routine%20health%20monitoring%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Dr%20Rao%20emphasises%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20one%20should%20check%20blood%20pressure%20at%20least%20once%20a%20year.%20The%20target%20should%20be%20a%20systolic%20pressure%20below%20130%20and%20a%20diastolic%20pressure%20below%2080.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20keeping%20cholesterol%20levels%20in%20check%20is%20crucial.%20%E2%80%9CA%20total%20cholesterol%20level%20should%20be%20below%20200%2C%20and%20LDL%20should%20always%20be%20less%20than%20100%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaintaining%20healthy%20sugar%20levels%20also%20plays%20a%20significant%20role%3A%20An%20LDL%20below%20100%2C%20a%20three-month%20average%20sugar%20level%20below%205.7%2C%20and%20a%20fasting%20blood%20sugar%20level%20below%20100%20is%20essential%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rao%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152523.508-1744019734.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152523.508-1744019734.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152523.508-1744019734-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152523.508-1744019734-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152523.508-1744019734-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152523.508-1744019734-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418283%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20essential%20to%20have%20a%20heart%20check-up%20every%20year%20post%2018%20years.%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealth-e.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2Fwhat-are-the-benefits-of-regular-heart-check-ups.webp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHealth-e%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20day-to-day%20level%2C%20these%20lifestyle%20changes%20can%20help%20prevent%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311579%2Fcardiologist-dr-deepak-krishnamurthy-breaks-myth-heart-attack-pain-relief-viral-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erisk%20of%20cardiac%20diseases%20effectively%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EExercise%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Walking%2010%2C000%20steps%20per%20day%20significantly%20reduces%20cardiovascular%20risks.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiet%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Avoid%20red%20meat%2C%20which%20is%20high%20in%20saturated%20fats%2C%20and%20instead%20consume%20polyunsaturated%20fatty%20acids%20found%20in%20sunflower%20and%20olive%20oil.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStress%20management%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yoga%20and%20meditation%20can%20help%20control%20stress%2C%20which%20is%20a%20silent%20contributor%20to%20heart%20disease.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Not%20all%20heart%20attacks%20result%20in%20cardiac%20arrest%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20confuse%20heart%20attacks%20with%20other%20cardiac%20conditions%20like%20sudden%20cardiac%20arrest%20or%20cardiomyopathy.%20Dr%20Rao%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CNot%20all%20cases%20of%20sudden%20collapse%20in%20the%20gym%20are%20due%20to%20heart%20attacks.%20There%20are%20other%20conditions%20like%20hypertrophic%20cardiomyopathy%20or%20ventricular%20arrhythmias%20that%20can%20cause%20sudden%20cardiac%20death.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20engaging%20in%20high-intensity%20workouts%2C%20he%20advises%20a%20thorough%20heart%20check-up.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20above%2040%2C%20or%20those%20with%20a%20family%20history%20of%20heart%20disease%2C%20diabetes%2C%20or%20hypertension%2C%20should%20undergo%20tests%20like%20ECG%20or%20treadmill%20tests%20before%20engaging%20in%20strenuous%20exercise.%E2%80%9D%20These%20tests%20help%20detect%20abnormalities%20in%20heart%20rhythm%2C%20blood%20flow%2C%20or%20stress-related%20changes%20that%20may%20signal%20underlying%20heart%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20in%20heart%20disease%20among%20young%20Indians%20is%20a%20pressing%20concern.%20While%20some%20factors%20like%20genetics%20cannot%20be%20controlled%2C%20lifestyle%20modifications%2C%20early%20detection%2C%20and%20routine%20monitoring%20can%20significantly%20reduce%20risks.%20As%20Dr%20Rao%20stresses%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20important%20step%20is%20primary%20prevention%20%E2%80%94%20preventing%20the%20disease%20before%20it%20occurs%20by%20maintaining%20optimal%20health%20markers%20and%20avoiding%20known%20risk%20factors%20like%20smoking%20and%20physical%20inactivity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20increasing%20awareness%2C%20proactive%20healthcare%2C%20and%20lifestyle%20changes%2C%20the%20alarming%20rise%20in%20heart%20attacks%20among%20young%20Indians%20can%20be%20curtailed%2C%20ensuring%20a%20healthier%20future%20for%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fxplore%2F2025%2FFeb%2F24%2F50-of-heart-attack-c