%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20business%20is%20called%20Secret%20Squirrel%20Consulting%20because%20a%20lot%20of%20intel%20analysts%20are%20called%20Secret%20Squirrels%20since%20we%20handle%20top-secret%20information.%20When%20I%20was%20in%20the%20military%2C%20I%20had%20to%20work%20with%20top-secret%20information%2C%20so%20for%20me%2C%20it's%20second%20nature%20to%20go%20from%20top-secret%20to%20regular%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20four%20tips%20I%20recommend%20for%20those%20looking%20to%20transition%20out%20of%20the%20federal%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a2f5a5e-d518-4654-80e2-32c41e94ec1e%5C%22%3E1.%20Figure%20out%20your%20skills%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20federal%20workers%20can%20go%20anywhere%20with%20their%20skills.%20They%20could%20go%20into%20nonprofits%2C%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20or%20contracting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tell%20people%20to%20first%20analyze%20their%20skills%20and%20figure%20out%20what%20skills%20they%20have%20that%20they%20want%20to%20continue%20using.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20in%20love%20with%20these%20big%20titles%2C%20but%20I%20tell%20them%2C%20maybe%20you%20can%20get%20a%20role%20as%20an%20individual%20contributor%20or%20as%20a%20program%20analyst%20and%20still%20make%20six%20figures.%20Don't%20just%20focus%20on%20the%20roles.%20Focus%20on%20the%20job%20description%20and%20the%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20those%20skills%2C%20make%20sure%20to%20highlight%20them%20on%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20and%20you'll%20have%20a%20better%20chance%20of%20getting%20recruiters%20to%20call%20you%20than%20if%20you%20just%20focus%20on%20a%20random%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b174ac1d-a1cf-4643-a7d2-96607cea94b6%5C%22%3E2.%20Cut%20it%20down%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20has%20time%20to%20read%20a%2015%2C%2020%2C%20or%2030-page%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20federal%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20are%20very%20long%20because%20when%20you%20go%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22ht