ias%2C%20with%20Musk%20labeling%20ChatGPT%20as%20%26quot%3Bwoke.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20latest%20family%20of%20AI%20models%2C%20Llama%204%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20answer%20more%20%26quot%3Bcontentious%26quot%3B%20topics%20like%20politics%20than%20its%20predecessor%2C%20the%20company%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20companies%20typically%20build%20guardrails%20so%20chatbots%2C%20like%20Meta's%20AI%20or%20ChatGPT%2C%20don't%20wade%20into%20overly%20controversial%20territory.%20It's%20a%20tricky%20balance%2C%20because%20too%20much%20prompt-dodging%20can%20annoy%20users%20or%20leave%20out%20important%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20said%20Llama%204%20is%20less%20likely%20to%20dodge%20hot-button%20questions.%20While%20the%20previous%20version%2C%20Llama%203.3%2C%20refused%20to%20answer%207%25%20of%20politically%20or%20socially%20charged%20prompts%2C%20Llama%204%20turns%20them%20down%20less%20than%202%25%20of%20the%20time%2C%20per%20Meta's%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20is%20also%20%26quot%3Bdramatically%20more%20balanced%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20prompts%20it%20refuses%2C%20Meta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Llama%204%20models%20consist%20of%20the%20Llama%204%20Scout%2C%20Llama%204%20Maverick%2C%20and%20Llama%204%20Behemoth.%20The%20Llama%204%20Scout%20and%20Llama%204%20Maverick%20were%20released%20on%20Saturday%2C%20while%20the%20Llama%204%20Behemoth%20is%20still%20training%2C%20Meta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Llama%204%20Scout%20and%20Llama%204%20Maverick%20were%20distilled%20from%20Llama%204%20Behemoth%2C%20which%20Meta%20said%20is%20its%20%26quot%3Bmost%20powerful%20yet%20and%20among%20the%20world's%20smartest%20LLMs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20tested%20Llama%204%20with%20a%20set%20of%20debated%20topical%20questions%20%E2%80%94%20ones%20in%20which%20people%20often%20take%20opposing%20sides.%20In%20these%20tests%2C%20Meta%20checked%20whether%20the%20model%20would%20answer%20one%20side%20but%20refuse%20the%20other.%2