%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-partner-ddn-strategic-leap-nvidia-ai-infrastructure-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomponents%20%3C%2Fa%3Erequired%20to%20generate%20depictions%20of%20everyone%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eas%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-studio-ghibli-image-generator-copyright-debate-sam-altman-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanime%20character%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20not%20exempt.%20For%20instance%2C%20an%20imported%20remote-controlled%20toy%20car%20with%20chips%20in%20both%20components%20would%20need%20an%20exception%20for%20toys%2C%20to%20avoid%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20still%20have%20more%20questions%20than%20answers%20about%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Morgan%20Stanley%20analysts%20in%20a%20note%20sent%20to%20investors%20Thursday%20morning.%20%26quot%3BSemiconductors%20are%20exempt.%20But%20what%20about%20modules%3F%20Cards%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Friday%20morning%2C%20analysts%20were%20still%20scratching%20their%20heads%20as%20to%20the%20impact%2C%20despite%20the%20exemption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20exactly%20sure%20what%20to%20do%20with%20all%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Bernstein's%20analysts.%20%26quot%3BMost%20semiconductors%20enter%20the%20US%20inside%20other%20things%20for%20which%20tariffs%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20much%20bigger%20influence%2C%20hence%20secondary%20effects%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20far%20more%20material.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22664b1f34-5e87-4acc-910e-9889df300831%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20needs%20lots%20of%20things%20that%20aren't%20exempt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20designs%20chips%20and%20software%2C%20but%20what%20it%20mainly%20sells%20are%20boards%2C%20according%20to%20Dylan%20Patel%2C%20chief%20analyst%20at%20Semianalysis.%20Boards%20contain%20multiple%20chips%2C%20but%20also%20power%20delivery%20controls%2C%20and%20other%20components%20to%20make%20them%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20surface%2C%20the%20exemption%20does%20not%20exempt%20Nvidia%20shipments%20as%20they%20ship%20GPU%20board%20assemblies%2C%26quot%3B%20Patel%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIf%20accelerator%20boards%20are%20excluded%20in%20addition%20to%20semiconductors%2C%20then%20the%20cost%20would%20not%20go%20up%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20boards%20are%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20bumper%20crop%20of%20AI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-data-center-colossus-power-memphis-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20works%20right%20now.%20Server%20racks%2C%20steel%20cabinets%2C%20and%20all%20the%20cabling%2C%20cooling%20gear%2C%20and%20switches%20to%20manage%20data%20flow%20and%20power%20are%20mostly%20imported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famd-lisa-su-ceo-nvidia-competition-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAMD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%2C%20like%20Nvidia%2C%20produces%20its%20AI%20chips%20in%20Taiwan%2C%20told%20BI%20the%20company%20is%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20semiconductors%20are%20exempt%20from%20the%20reciprocal%20tariffs%2C%20we%20are%20assessing%20the%20details%20and%20any%20impacts%20on%20our%20broader%20customer%20and%20partner%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20an%20email%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20implications%20of%20the%20tariffs.%20But%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20got%20the%20question%20from%20financial%20analysts%20last%20month%20at%20the%20company's%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-things-key-takeaways-nvidia-gtc-conference-this-year-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20annual%20GTC%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20preparing%20and%20we%20have%20been%20preparing%20to%20manufacture%20onshore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Taiwanese%20manufacturer%20TSMC%20has%20invested%20%24100%20billion%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-us-factories-wont-erase-reliance-taiwan-made-advanced-chips-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanufacturing%20facility%20in%20Arizona%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20now%20running%20production%20silicon%20in%20Arizona.%20And%20so%2C%20we%20will%20manufacture%20onshore.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20systems%2C%20we'll%20manufacture%20as%20much%20onshore%20as%20we%20need%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20super%20agile%20supply%20chain%2C%20we're%20manufacturing%20in%20so%20many%20different%20places%2C%20we%20could%20shift%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20potentially%20producing%20chips%20in%20the%20US%2C%20it's%20plausible%20that%20companies%2C%20including%20Nvidia%2C%20could%20do%20more%20of%20their%20final%20assembly%20in%20the%20US%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-taiwan-china-chip-war-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EChris%20Miller%2C%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BChip%20War%26quot%3B%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20leading%20expert%20on%20the%20semiconductor%20industry%20told%20BI.%20Moving%20the%20later%20steps%20of%20the%20manufacturing%20process%20to%20un-tariffed%20shores%2C%20which%20right%20now%20include%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20as%20well%20as%20the%20US%2C%20could%20theoretically%20allow%20these%20companies%20to%20import%20bare%20silicon%20chips%20and%20avoid%20levies.%20But%20that%20change%20would%20come%20with%20a%20cost%20as%20well%2C%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20retaliatory%20tariffs%20rolling%20in%2C%20US%20manufacturers%20could%20find%20tariffs%20weighing%20down%20demand%20in%20international%20markets%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2