a.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fstock-market-crash-live-updates-sensex-slides-3-000-points-amid-trump-tariff-bloodbath-8106569%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20While%20I'm%20Alive%26quot%3B%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20On%20Top%20Court%20Order%20Sacking%20Teachers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVowing%20to%20protect%20the%20jobs%20of%20'deserving'%20teachers%20whose%20appointment%20was%20cancelled%20by%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20today%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20the%20all-India%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20NEET%20and%20said%20the%20top%20court%20did%20not%20cancel%20the%20whole%20examination%20in%20that%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20must%20clarify%20who%20is%20deserving%20and%20who%20is%20not.%20Give%20us%20the%20list.%20No%20one%20has%20the%20right%20to%20break%20the%20education%20system.%20In%20the%20Vyapam%20case%20in%20BJP-ruled%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20so%20many%20people%20were%20killed.%20They%20have%20not%20got%20justice%20till%20today.%20In%20NEET%2C%20many%20allegations%20surfaced.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20did%20not%20cancel%20the%20examination.%20Why%20is%20Bengal%20being%20targeted%3F%20We%20want%20to%20know.%20You%20are%20scared%20of%20Bengal's%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20a%20gathering%20of%20sacked%20teachers%20at%20Kolkata's%20Netaji%20Indoor%20Stadium.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20provides%20us%20clarity%2C%20we%20will%20be%20grateful.%20If%20not%2C%20we%20will%20find%20a%20way%20and%20stand%20by%20you.%20Suffer%20for%20two%20months%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20suffer%20for%2020%20years.%20And%20I%20will%20compensate%20for%20those%20two%20months%20too.%20You%20won't%20have%20to%20beg%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20week%20cancelled%20the%20appointments%20of%20more%20than%2025%2C000%20teachers%20and%20school%20staff%20recruited%20by%20the%20West%20Bengal%20School%20Service%20Commission%20in%202016%20after%20large-scale%20irregularities%20were%20found%20in%20the%20recruitment%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20legal%20precedents%2C%20the%20court%20said%20this%20is%20a%20case%20%26quot%3Bwherein%20the%20entire%20selection%20process%20has%20been%20vitiated%20and%20tainted%20beyond%20resolution.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BManipulations%20and%20frauds%20on%20a%20large%20scale%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20attempted%20cover-up%2C%20have%20dented%20the%20selection%20process%20beyond%20repair%20and%20partial%20redemption.%20The%20credibility%20and%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20selection%20are%20denuded%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Sanjeev%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20said%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20noted%20that%20the%20School%20Service%20Commission%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20candid%20enough%20to%20admit%3B%20(i)%20rank%20jumping%2C%20that%20is%2C%20to%20say%20candidates%20having%20lower%20rank%20were%20preferred%20over%20those%20having%20higher%20rank%2C%20(ii)%20out%20of%20panel%20appointments%2C%20that%20is%2C%20candidates%20who%20are%20not%20in%20the%20panel%20of%20shortlisted%20candidates%20have%20been%20recommended%20and%20appointed%2C%20(iii)%20candidates%20who%20were%20not%20recommended%20by%20WBSSC%20were%20appointed%20by%20the%20Board%2C%20and%20(iv)%20manipulation%20of%20the%20OMR%20scores%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20School%20Service%20Commission%20had%20destroyed%20the%20OMR%20sheets%20and%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20justification%26quot%3B%20for%20this%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20spite%20of%20the%20factual%20background%20and%20the%20credible%20evidence%20indicating%20irregularities%2C%20WBSSC%20initially%20did%20try%20and%20cover%20up%20the%20lapses%20and%20illegalities.%20The%20cover%20up%20itself%20has%20made%20the%20verification%20and%20ascertainment%20more%20difficult%20or%20rather%20impossible%20given%20the%20scale%20of%20camouflage%20and%20dressing%20up%20done%20at%20each%20stage.%20We%20are%20convinced%20that%20the%20entire%20selection%20process%20was%20intentionally%20compromised%20due%20to%20the%20illegalities%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20candidates%20not%20found%20to%20be%20tainted%20won't%20need%20to%20refund%20salaries%20they%20received%20through%20the%20years%2C%20but%20their%20services%20will%20be%20terminated.%20The%20court%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20repeat%20the%20recruitment%20process%20in%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20fire%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20responded%20by%20accusing%20Opposition%20parties%20BJP%20and%20CPM%20of%20hatching%20a%20conspiracy%20aimed%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bcollapse%20of%20the%20state%20education%20system%26quot%3B.%20Targeting%20the%20rivals%20today%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20people%20everywhere.%20But%20don't%20snatch%20jobs%20from%20teachers%20to%20target%20me.%20Remember%2C%20an%20injured%20tiger%20is%20more%20dangerous.%20It's%20an%20attack%20on%20our%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20accept%20the%20court's%20order%2C%20seek%20clarification%20and%20file%20a%20review%20petition%20too.%20You%20have%20not%20received%20a%20termination%20letter%2C%20so%20you%20keep%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20asking%20the%20teachers%20to%20continue%20working.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20teachers%20at%20the%20gathering%20said%20they%20won't%20take%20an%20exam%20again%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20job.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20file%20a%20review%20petition%20and%20we%20will%20urge%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20and%20School%20Service%20Commission%20to%20file%20review%20petitions%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20a%