bed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20Milan%20refused%20to%20accept%20society%E2%80%99s%20limited%20expectations.%20Where%20others%20saw%20a%20diagnosis%2C%20she%20saw%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20brilliance.%20With%20the%20support%20of%20her%20extended%20family%2C%20she%20built%20an%20inclusive%2C%20nurturing%20space%20where%20Samar%20could%20grow%2C%20not%20despite%20his%20neurodivergence%20but%20because%20of%20it.%20Whether%20it%20was%20encouraging%20his%20love%20for%20baking%2C%20cheering%20him%20on%20through%20his%20travels%2C%20or%20helping%20him%20share%20his%20life%20online%2C%20Milan%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358168%2Fpeople-with-nonspeaking-autism-in-india-talking-fingers-book-authors-padma-jyothi-chitra-paul%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eempowered%3C%2Fa%3E%20Samar%20to%20be%20visible%2C%20expressive%2C%20and%20proud%20of%20who%20he%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20society%20where%20stigma%20still%20shadows%20autism%2C%20her%20journey%20is%20both%20bold%20and%20deeply%20necessary.%20She%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20just%20advocate%20for%20her%20child%20%E2%80%94%20she%20advocates%20for%20every%20child%20who%E2%80%99s%20ever%20been%20misunderstood%20and%20every%20parent%20who%E2%80%99s%20ever%20felt%20alone.%20Her%20work%20reminds%20us%20that%20neurodivergent%20children%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cfixed%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20they%20need%20to%20be%20accepted%2C%20supported%2C%20and%20celebrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilan%E2%80%99s%20mission%20goes%20beyond%20her%20household.%20Through%20counselling%2C%20activism%2C%20and%20public%20speaking%2C%20she%E2%80%99s%20educating%20families%2C%20breaking%20taboos%2C%20and%20reshaping%20conversations%20around%20invisible%20disabilities%20in%20India.%20Her%20message%20is%20clear%3A%20every%20child%2C%20regardless%20of%20how%20they%20experience%20the%20world%2C%20deserves%20dignity%2C%20love%2C%20and%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20Milan%20and%20Samar%20are%20not%20just%20spreading%20awareness%2C%20they%20are%20building%20a%20movement%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20replaces%20silence%20with%20dialogue%2C%20stigma%20with%20pride%2C%20and%20fear%20with%20fierce%2C%20joyful%20advocacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Vidya%20Gowri%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743852600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1-1743838137.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D417965%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20mother%E2%80%99s%20love%2C%20activism%2C%20and%20courage%20are%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20autism%20awareness%20and%20acceptance%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Samreen%20Syed%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F417965%2Fmilan-singh-autism-awareness-motherhood-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blog%3A%20Love%20You%2C%20But%20I'll%20Sleep%20At%20Mine%3A%20On%20Couples%20Who%20'Live%20Apart%20Together'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EI%20met%20Aisha%20and%20Sidharth%20on%20a%20train%20journey%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20mundane%20but%20ended%20up%20feeling%20like%20an%20episode%20of%20a%20really%20juicy%20reality%20show.%20We%20were%20in%20the%20same%20cabin%2C%20and%20while%20I%20was%20just%20trying%20to%20zone%20out%20with%20my%20playlist%2C%20they%20were%20having%20a%20passionate%20discussion%20about%20something%20that%20was%20clearly%20important.%20Not%20the%20'who-left-the-wet-towel-on-the-bed'%20kind%20of%20argument.%20This%20was%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20you%2C%20but%20I%20love%20my%20own%20space%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Aisha%20said%2C%20dramatically%20flipping%20her%20hair%20as%20if%20she%20were%20in%20a%20Bollywood%20monologue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExactly!%26quot%3B%20Sidharth%20said%2C%20equally%20animated%2C%20before%20noticing%20me%20staring.%20%26quot%3BSorry%2C%20we%20are%20just%20talking%20about%20our%20relationship%20setup.%20We%20are%20married%20but%20do%20not%20live%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20that%20got%20my%20attention.%20As%20one%20of%20those%20'nosy'%20journalists%2C%20I%20could%20not%20resist.%20%26quot%3BWait.%20You%20are%20married%20but...%20live%20separately%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes!%20It%20is%20called%20Living%20Apart%20Together%2C%20or%20LAT%2C%26quot%3B%20Aisha%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20doing%20it%20for%20three%20years%2C%20and%20honestly%2C%20it%20is%20the%20best%20decision%20we%20ever%20made.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20is%20how%20I%20found%20myself%20falling%20down%20the%20rabbit%20hole%20of%20one%20of%20the%20most%20intriguing%20relationship%20trends%20out%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EModern%20Love%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20face%20it%3A%20romantic%20relationships%20aren't%20what%20they%20used%20to%20be.%20The%20old%2C%20predictable%20trajectory-meet%2C%20date%2C%20marry%2C%20move%20in%20together%2C%20have%20kids%2C%20and%20live%20happily%20ever%20after%20(or%20at%20least%20give%20it%20a%20shot)-no%20longer%20holds.%20Today%2C%20couples%20are%20customising%20relationships%20to%20fit%20their%20lifestyles%2C%20and%20the%20options%20are%20endless.%20Some%20choose%20ethical%20non-monogamy%2C%20where%20partners%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20explore%20romantic%20connections%20beyond%20their%20primary%20relationship.%20Others%20find%20themselves%20in%20'cuffing%20season'%20relationships-short-term%20relationships%20wherein%20people%20pair%20up%20around%20big%20holidays%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20companionship%2C%20only%20to%20fizzle%20out%20once%20the%20social%20calendars%20get%20over.%20Then%2C%20there%20is%20the%20growing%20wave%20of%20platonic%20partnerships%2C%20where%20best%20friends%20commit%20to%20life%20together%20without%20the%20romantic%20element.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20there%20is%20Living%20Apart%20Together%20(LAT)%2C%20the%20middle%20ground%20between%20traditional%20cohabitation%20and%20total%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Rage%20That%20Is%20LAT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20Apart%20Together%2C%20or%20LAT%2C%20is%20exactly%20what%20it%20sounds%20like%3A%20committed%20couples%20choosing%20to%20stay%20in%20separate%20homes%20instead%20of%20sharing%20a%20single%20space.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20'we%20need%20a%20break'%20situation%2C%20or%20some%20elite%20fad%20(although%2C%20let%20us%20be%20honest%2C%20it%20does%20require%20some%20financial%20flexibility).%20It%20is%20a%20conscious%20decision%20to%20be%20together%2C%20but%20not%20'too%20together'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Aisha%20and%20Sidharth%2C%20it%20was%20about%20preserving%20individuality%20while%20maintaining%20intimacy.%20They%20spent%20weekends%20together%2C%20had%20date%20nights%2C%20and%20even%20took%20vacations%20as%20a%20couple.%20But%20come%20Monday%20morning%2C%20they%20each%20went%20back%20to%20their%20respective%20homes%2C%20where%20they%20did%20not%20have%20to%20fight%20over%20toothpaste%20caps%20or%20thermostat%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20not%20alone.%20From%20Gen%20Z%20couples%20who%20grew%20up%20romanticising%20independence%20to%20older%20pairs%20rediscovering%20personal%20space%2C%20LAT%20is%20becoming%20a%20legitimate%20lifestyle%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20I%20start%20selling%20this%20concept%20like%20a%20late-night%20infomercial%2C%20there%20are%20things%20that%20make%20it%20work%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20that%20might%20make%20it...%20well%2C%20a%20logistical%20nightmare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Upsides%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Less%20Drama%2C%20More%20Romance%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Let%20us%20be%20real%3A%20nothing%20kills%20the%20excitement%20of%20a%20relationship%20like%20discovering%20that%20your%20partner%20chews%20loudly%20or%20leaves%20socks%20everywhere.%20Living%20separately%20means%20keeping%20the%20mystery%20alive.%20You%20get%20the%20butterflies%20of%20a%20date%20night%20without%20the%20horror%20of%20realising%20they%20hoard%20old%20pizza%20boxes%20%26quot%3Bfor%20sentimental%20reasons%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndependence%20Is%20Sexy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Aisha%2C%20who%20has%20always%20been%20fiercely%20independent%2C%20said%20she%20did%20not%20want%20to%20lose%20herself%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bwe%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20relationship.%20With%20LAT%2C%20she%20has%20her%20own%20space%20to%20work%2C%20unwind%2C%20and%20live%20life%20on%20her%20own%20terms%20while%20still%20having%20a%20partner%20to%20share%20experiences%20with.%20It%20is%20like%20having%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds%20without%20the%20messy%20roommate%20dynamics.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20Appreciation%2C%20Less%20Annoyance%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BAbsence%20makes%20the%20heart%20grow%20fonder%26quot%3B%20is%20not%20just%20a%20cliche%2C%20it%20is%20science.%20Seeing%20your%20partner%20only%20when%20you%20want%20to%2C%20rather%20than%20because%20you%20have%20to%2C%20means%20fewer%20petty%20fights%20and%20more%20quality%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20More%20Battles%20Over%20Home%20Decor%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sidharth%20loves%20minimalist%20spaces%2C%20while%20Aisha%20cannot%20resist%20a%20neon%20pink%20throw%20pillow.%20Thanks%20to%20LAT%2C%20their%20separate%20homes%20reflect%20their%20personalities%20without%20compromise.%20No%20one%20has%20to%20argue%20about%20whether%20a%20bean%20bag%20counts%20as%20%26quot%3Bserious%20furniture%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20are%20those%20less%20glamorous%20sides%20of%20LAT.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20Is%20Expensive%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETwo%20homes%20means%20two%20rents%2C%20two%20electricity%20bills%2C%20and%20two%20internet%20subscriptions.%20If%20you%20are%20not%20financially%20prepared%2C%20LAT%20could%20be%20more%20stressful%20than%20peaceful.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20About%20Kids%3F%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20you%20are%20planning%20to%20start%20a%20family%2C%20LAT%20gets%20complicated.%20Sure%2C%20some%20couples%20make%20it%20work%2C%20but%20coordinating%20school%20runs%2C%20doctor%20appointments%2C%20and%20bedtime%20routines%20from%20separate%20homes%20is%20no%20fun.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20Everyone%20Gets%20It%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BOh%2C%20so%20you%20guys%20are%2C%20like%2C%20not%20really%20together%3F%26quot%3B%20Aisha%20and%20Sidharth%20had%20heard%20this%20a%20million%20times.%20People%20assume%20LAT%20means%20a%20relationship%20is%20in%20trouble%20when%20in%20reality%2C%20it%20is%20often%20a%20very%20intentional%20choice.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Logistics%20Can%20Get%20Messy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Forgot%20your%20charger%20at%20their%20place%3F%20Need%20to%20coordinate%20who%20buys%20groceries%20for%20the%20weekend%3F%20Deciding%20where%20to%20celebrate%20Diwali%3F%20LAT%20requires%20a%20level%20of%20organisation%20that%20not%20all%20couples%20are%20ready%20for.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20About%20the%20Singles%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20when%20I%20thought%20I%20had%20heard%20all%20perspectives%2C%20my%20friend%20Priya%20chimed%20in%20with%20a%20take%20so%20good%20I%20almost%20choked%20on%20my%20coffee.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20basically%2C%20single%20people%20are%20also%20in%20LAT%20with%20the%20world%2C%20just...%20by%20default%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BLike%2C%20we%20live%20separately%20from%20our%20potential%20partners%2C%20we%20go%20on%20dates%2C%20and%20we%20get%20the%20space%20we%20need.%20The%20only%20difference%20is%20that%20we%20do%20not%20have%20a%20permanent%20'together'%20part%20of%20the%20equation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20she%20has%20a%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20LAT%20couples%20make%20a%20conscious%20choice%20to%20keep%20their%20independence%20intact%2C%20most%20single%20people%20have%20been%20doing%20it%20forever-just%20without%20the%20branding.%20Maybe%20that%20is%20why%20some%20singles%20do%20not%20feel%20the%20pressure%20to%20rush%20into%20traditional%20cohabiting%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoint%20being%2C%20LAT%20is%20not%20for%20everyone.%20If%20you%20love%20waking%20up%20next%20to%20your%20partner%20every%20morning%2C%20then%20it%20might%20sound%20absurd.%20But%20for%20people%20like%20Aisha%20and%20Sidharth%2C%20it%20is%20the%20perfect%20balance%20between%20commitment%20and%20personal%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnd%20then%20there%20is%20me.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomewhere%20between%20listening%20to%20Aisha%20and%20Sidharth's%20story%20and%20Priya's%20single-person%20LAT%20realisation%2C%20I%20had%20a%20moment%20of%20clarity.%20Turns%20out%2C%20I%20have%20been%20in%20an%20LAT%20relationship%20without%20even%20realising%20it.%20My%20partner%20is%20a%20wedding%20planner%2C%20and%20I%20am%20a%20lifestyle%20journalist.%20We%20both%20travel%20for%20work-sometimes%20for%20weeks%2C%20even%20months-constantly%20hopping%20between%20cities.%20We%20do%20not%20get%20to%20do%20the%20usual%20'couple'%20activities%20every%20day.%20But%20here%20is%20the%20thing%2C%20it%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20keep%20our%20communication%20flowing%2C%20sending%20each%20other%20updates%20about%20our%20day%2C%20our%20work%2C%20and%20our%20travels.%20And%20when%20we%20finally%20meet%2C%20it%20is%20not%20routine%2C%20it%20is%20exciting-a%20reminder%20for%20why%20we%20chose%20each%20other%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20maybe%20LAT%20is%20not%20a%20trend%3B%20it%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20many%20ways%20love%20adapts%20to%20the%20world%20we%20live%20in.%20And%20if%20it%20keeps%20people%20happier%2C%20who%20is%20to%20say%20it%20is%20not%20the%20future%20of%20relationships%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubham%20Bhatnagar%20is%20the%20Editor%20at%20NDTV%20Food%20and%20Travel.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743833460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F8eblnqc_lat_625x300_04_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Flove-you-but-ill-sleep-at-mine-on-couples-who-live-apart-together-8087499%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20not%20a%20we-need-a-break%20situation%2C%20or%20some%20elite%20fad%20(although%2C%20let%20us%20be%20honest%2C%20it%20does%20require%20some%20financial%20flexibility).%20'Living%20apart%20together'%20is%20a%20conscious%20decision%20to%20be%20together%2C%20but%20not%20'too'%20together.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Flove-you-but-ill-sleep-at-mine-on-couples-who-live-apart-together-8087499%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20The%20Man%20Who%20Grew%20300%20Mango%20Varieties%20on%20a%20Single%20Tree%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKalimullah%20Khan%20wa